bias.explanation: Daily Bias is Bearish based on previous day (Bearish), Asia (Bullish), and London (Bullish) with weighted by session range. US Open Bias is Bullish. Overnight range position is Inside. Gap is small down. HTF slope bias is n/a. Volatility regime is 'normal', momentum and ROC aligned at -0.002, RVOL at 0.26. News tone is neutral and only adjusts confidence, not direction. Day impact: Session weighting favors larger-range sessions over quieter ones. ATR-scaled thresholds reduce false bias on quiet days. US open inside overnight range favors mean reversion early. HTF zones suggest Bullish bias (score 1.90; Bullish zones: 4, Bearish zones: 3.).
